{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b31bfa3b56","title":"对武汉事件的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c69c3abba2","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"b31bfa3b56"}],"tags":[{"id":"0d8f653275","name":"武汉地区无产阶级革命派百万雄师联络站（百万雄师）","type":"人物"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33bb3f3618","type":"paragraph","text":"四、要向左派作工作，不要乘机报复五、要馨惕坏人揭乱，不许破坏社会秩序。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"9a478aaf73","type":"paragraph","text":"对武汉事件的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"a8bbeeb9bb","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月）本来军内的问题没有机会解决，武汉问题发生了，就有机会解决了，机会是他们给的。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"587d4225da","type":"paragraph","text":"XX","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"3db0345afa","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"d6284a245c","type":"paragraph","text":"全国都应该从武汉事件中学习。全国支持武汉地区，武汉地区的斗争推动了全国的工作。一年来发生了天翻地复的变化，当然有点乱。这里乱那里也乱，没有什么关系。象武汉这是很好的事，矛盾暴露了就好解决。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"799b4529f8","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉一小搬人的频变行为可以使全国的解放军、革命造反派、群众组织从中得到教育这次文化大革命损失是最小最小最小的，成绩是最大最大最大的。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"e0a473f11c","type":"paragraph","text":"X十","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"b828e7a902","type":"paragraph","text":"X对“百万雄师”一个也不抓，几个坏头头让他们自己检举。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"196fee99b9","type":"paragraph","text":"关于“八一”建军节的指示","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"11e216e812","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月）","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"fb142d3c6c","type":"paragraph","text":"“八一”不能改，这是很重要的一天。我们打响了第一枪，为井岗山的斗争揭开了序幕。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"717b303f5a","type":"paragraph","text":"这个问题是历史问题，历史问题是不容题倒的。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"461bb6ab60","type":"paragraph","text":"为一九六七年七月开日《人民日报》","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"3dcab2b2bc","type":"paragraph","text":"社加的一句斋","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"e4e4fecc26","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月）团结一致，同心同德，任何强大的敌人，任何困难的坏境，都会向我们投降的。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"},{"id":"a30c41d26c","type":"paragraph","text":"321","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56"}],"page":{"id":"c00b7328c8","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b31bfa3b56","start":334,"end":334}}}},"__N_SSG":true}